AN ACT CONCERNING FUNDING FOR EMERGENCY HOUSING.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 That the sum of one million five hundred thousand dollars be
2 appropriated to Continuum of Care, Inc. from the General Fund, for the
3 fiscal year ending June 30, 2027, for the operation of the emergency
4 housing program.
Statement of Purpose:
To fund Continuum of Care, Inc.'s emergency housing program.
